---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technique Library - Surf Deeper" description="Step-by-step surf techniques, from paddling efficiently to riding the pocket. Learn from the community.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Technique Library</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Master the fundamentals and advanced techniques</p>
  </header>

  <section class="technique-categories">
    <h2>Technique Categories</h2>
    <div class="category-grid">
      <div class="category-card">
        <h3>Paddling</h3>
        <p>Efficient paddling techniques for catching waves and positioning</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Basic paddling form</li>
          <li>Duck diving</li>
          <li>Paddle positioning</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="category-card">
        <h3>Pop-up</h3>
        <p>Getting to your feet quickly and smoothly</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Beginner pop-up</li>
          <li>Advanced pop-up variations</li>
          <li>Pop-up timing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="category-card">
        <h3>Wave Riding</h3>
        <p>Techniques for riding different parts of the wave</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Bottom turns</li>
          <li>Top turns</li>
          <li>Cutbacks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="category-card">
        <h3>Advanced Moves</h3>
        <p>Progressive techniques for experienced surfers</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Aerials</li>
          <li>Barrel riding</li>
          <li>Tube riding</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="coming-soon">
    <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
    <p>We're building a comprehensive library of surf techniques with step-by-step guides, video tutorials, and community contributions. Each technique will include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>üìù Detailed written instructions</li>
      <li>üé• Video demonstrations</li>
      <li>‚ö†Ô∏è Common mistakes to avoid</li>
      <li>üí° Pro tips from experienced surfers</li>
      <li>üìä Difficulty ratings</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="contribute-cta">
    <h2>Share Your Knowledge</h2>
    <p>Have a technique you've mastered? Share it with the community and help others improve their surfing.</p>
    <a href="/contribute" class="cta-button">Contribute a Technique</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .technique-categories h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .category-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .category-card {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .category-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .category-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .category-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .category-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .category-card li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .category-card li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .coming-soon {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .coming-soon h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coming-soon li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contribute-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #00ff88;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .contribute-cta h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contribute-cta p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #00ff88;
    color: #0f172a;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #00cc6a;
  }
</style>
